OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FWhen Scotland face Haiti in their
OL,8,Ffirst World Cup clash later this
OL,9,Fmonth, it won't just be the Tartan
OL,10,FArmy getting to see their team compete
OL,11,Fin the tournament for the first time
OL,12,Fin a generation, as ITV News US
OL,13,FCorrespondent reports
OL,15,FAdditional reporting by Washington
OL,16,FProducer Joshua Brooks
OL,18,FFor the football-mad boys of Port-au-
OL,19,FPrince, the next month promises to be
OL,20,Fone of unparalleled excitement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
