OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FSadly, Haiti's chances look slim, with
OL,8,Fa tough group including Brazil,
OL,9,FScotland and Morocco.
OL,11,FBut older Haitians remember the epic
OL,12,Fmoment in 1974 when Emmanuel Sanon's
OL,13,Fleft foot put them briefly ahead
OL,14,Fagainst Italy, before the Europeans
OL,15,Ffought back, ultimately beating them 3-
OL,16,F1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
