PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780582265
OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FThe prospect of another World Cup goal
OL,8,Flies partly with their star striker
OL,9,FFrantzdy Pierrot, who was recently
OL,10,Fhonoured at a special ceremony in
OL,11,FBoston.
OL,13,FThe event reflected his childhood in
OL,14,FMassachusetts after his parents left
OL,15,Ftheir Caribbean home.
OL,17,FPierrot isn't just a role model for
OL,18,Faspiring footballers in Haiti. He has
OL,19,Falso set up a foundation to support
OL,20,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780582265
OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FWhen I asked him about the legacy that
OL,8,Fhe hopes this World Cup will leave on
OL,9,Fthe island, he said: "For us, we are
OL,10,Fgoing to try to do everything we can
OL,11,Fto make the country proud, to make
OL,12,Fthem proud. We know that we are one of
OL,13,Fthe things they look up to, in a
OL,14,Fpositive way with everything that is
OL,15,Fgoing on in the country," Pierrot said.
OL,17,F"I know all the kids are going to look
OL,18,Fup to us and we must do everything we
OL,19,Fcan to make them proud."
OL,26,@qD@VOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
