PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780582265
OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FAmong those watching the ceremony to
OL,8,Facknowledge his achievement was his
OL,9,Ffather, Justin Pierrot.
OL,11,F"It means a lot for Haiti. I am
OL,12,Ffeeling proud of him. I am feeling
OL,13,Fgreat. In Haiti, we love football, but
OL,14,Fthere are plenty of challenges over
OL,15,Fthere," Justin said.
OL,17,FHe lamented that more Haitians can't
OL,18,Fcome to the World Cup.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780582265
OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,F"There is regret more Haitians are not
OL,8,Fcoming, because it costs a lot of
OL,9,Fmoney. Many of them will have to watch
OL,10,Fon TV," he added.
OL,12,FThe example Pierrot is setting isn't
OL,13,Fthe only beacon of hope for Haiti this
OL,14,Fsummer.
OL,16,FA pop song offering a refreshing
OL,17,Fwindow into the more positive side of
OL,18,Fthe island has also been released,
OL,19,Fwhich the performers hope will become
OL,20,Fan anthem for all the underdog teams
OL,21,Fin the tournament.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
