OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe accompanying video shows vibrant
OL,13,Fscenes of the island at odds with the
OL,14,Ftypical images seen on news bulletins
OL,15,Fof violence and poverty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
