PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780582265
OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FSinger Sincerely Suav tells me he
OL,8,Fwants "a song that people can cheer
OL,9,Fto, that people can sing along to,
OL,10,Fbecause we take a lot of pride in
OL,11,Fthat. This is a beautiful moment for
OL,12,FHaiti, for people in Haiti".
OL,14,FHaiti is the poorest nation to qualify
OL,15,Ffor this year's World Cup, but it is
OL,16,Fentering the tournament in a spirit of
OL,17,Foptimism.
OL,19,FAs they saw in 1974, miracles do
OL,20,Fhappen, even if they are ephemeral
OL,21,Fmoments of hope.
