OL,3,C'It'll change everything': Poverty-
OL,4,Cstricken Haiti yearns for World Cup
OL,5,Cglory
OL,7,FAny goal for Haiti in this event will
OL,8,Fbe a cause for national celebration; a
OL,9,Fchance to show the world that, despite
OL,10,Fits profound challenges, this country
OL,11,Fcan compete on a global stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
